Package: epishiny.template
Title: Template for Building Standalone 'epishiny' Module Packages
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Paul", "Campbell", , "paul.campbell@epicentre.msf.org",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1018-6606"))
Description: A starter package for authoring additional 'epishiny' modules as
    standalone R packages. Keeps the core 'epishiny' package small while
    letting downstream module packages share its conventions, options, and
    cross-module reactive plumbing. Deliberately does *not* depend on
    'epishiny' itself: small helpers are mirrored locally so a child module
    can be installed without pulling in 'epishiny''s heavier visualisation
    dependencies (e.g. 'leaflet', 'sf', 'highcharter'). Replace the package
    name, the placeholder module ('mymodule_ui'/'mymodule_server'), the
    asset path prefix and the metadata in this file before publishing.
